=== Noun ===
{{en-noun2|'''pig'''|'''[[pigs]] '''or''' [[swine]]'''}}
#A [[mammal]] of the genus ''[[Sus]]'', often raised on [[farm]]s for [[meat]]. Scientific name: [[Sus scrofa]], [[Sus scrofa domesticus]].
#A [[greedy]] person; someone who overeats or has eats rapidly and noisily.
#A [[nasty]] or [[disgusting]] person; as, a ''[[capitalist]] pig'', ''[[male chauvinist pig]]''.
#A [[dirty]] person.
#(''derogatory slang'') A [[police officer]].
#A [[difficult]] [[problem]].
#When used attributively in certain [[set phrase]]s: [[imitation|Imitation]], not [[real]]; as, ''[[pig Latin]]'', ''[[pig iron]]''.

